Resource Profile: Cancer Patient Profile

Official URL: http://luisfabib.github.io/onconova/StructureDefinition/onconova-cancer-patient Version: 0.1.0
Active as of 2025-10-15 Computable Name: OnconovaCancerPatient

A profile representing a cancer patient with specific extensions and constraints for the Onconova use case. Due to the research-scope of Onconova, the patient information is anonymized and identifying data elements are not provided.

It constrains the mCODE CancerPatient profile to ensure anonymity of the patient information and to introduce additional Onconova-specific case information. Any Patient resource complying with the US Core Patient or mCODE CancerPatient profiles will also comply with this profile.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: Karnofsky Performance Status Profile, Adverse Event Profile, Aneuploid Score Profile, Cancer Risk Assessment Profile... Show 29 more, Cancer Stage, Comorbidities Profile, ECOG Performance Status Profile, Genomic Variant Profile, Homologous Recombination Deficiency Profile, Imaging Disease Status Profile, Lifestyle Profile, Loss of Heterozygosity Profile, Medication Administration Profile, Microsatellite Instability Profile, Primary Cancer Condition Profile, Radiotherapy Summary Profile, Secondary Cancer Condition Profile, Serum Tumor Marker Level Category, Surgical Procedure Profile, Therapy Line Profile, TNM Distant Metastases Category, TNM Grade Category, TNM Lymphatic Invasion Category, TNM Perineural Invasion Category, TNM Primary Tumor Category, TNM Regional Nodes Category, TNM Residual Tumor Category, TNM Stage Group, Tumor Board Review, Tumor Marker Profile, Tumor Mutational Burden Profile, Tumor Neoantigen Burden Profile and Venous Invasion Category
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: Onconova FHIR REST Capability Statement
